# nexus /.meta — META engine surface SSOT
# nexus 는 본질적으로 META engine — atlas_meta_dashboard, drill_batch, ω-cycle 자기-발견.
# raw 90 META-witness pattern 적용.
# Created 2026-04-27.
#
# 5-repo convergence (META 가 first-class engine):
#   nexus      27 roadmap_* + atlas_meta_dashboard.md + tool/lockdown/meta_lockdown.hexa
#   hexa-lang  tool/hx_meta.hexa (16 subcommands)
#   n6         tool/n6_meta.hexa (20 subcommands, 12 declared scanners)
#   anima      14 proposal_* tools
#   airgenome  bin/ag_meta + scanners/*.meta.hexa
# nexus 는 5/5 convergence 의 일원이지만 .meta 선언이 없었음 — 이 파일이 그 부재를 채움.

meta-policy 1 new "self-modify boundary"
  slug meta-self-modify-boundary
  enforce-layer hive-agent
  enforce-layer-rationale META observes + proposes; locked SSOT mutations 은 raw 1 unlock-relock + raw 85 sec-escalation-audit-trail-witness 경유. apply-gate 는 human-in-loop. continuous-scan 은 launchd cadence — META 는 enforce 하지 않고 observe 만, 따라서 kernel hook 불필요.

  # SSOTs META MAY propose-but-not-directly-mutate (locked targets):
  self-modify-deny .own                         # raw 1 os-lock; raw 20 own-monotonic
  self-modify-deny .meta                        # this file — 일단 schema lock 후
  self-modify-deny .roadmap                     # raw 1 os-lock; raw 88 roadmap-transition-witness
  self-modify-deny .turn                        # raw 1 os-lock 확장 (week 7-12 of raw 89 ramp)
  self-modify-deny .end                         # raw 1 os-lock 확장 (60d of raw 90 ramp)
  self-modify-deny .ext                         # raw 1 os-lock; raw 14 ext-ssot
  self-modify-deny .command                     # raw 1 os-lock 확장 (raw 83 follow-up)
  self-modify-deny .chain                       # raw 1 os-lock 확장
  self-modify-deny project.hexa                 # raw 1 os-lock
  self-modify-deny n6/atlas.n6                  # n6-architecture canonical, READ + APPEND only via witness_emit
  self-modify-deny n6/atlas.signals.n6          # n6-architecture canonical, READ-ONLY (.guide convention)
  self-modify-deny n6/atlas.millennium.n6       # n6-architecture canonical, READ-ONLY (.guide convention)
  self-modify-deny tool/witness_emit.hexa       # canonical witness path
  self-modify-deny tool/atlas_absorb_*.hexa     # .own atlas-absorb-mandatory layer 1+2+3 의 trinity
  self-modify-deny shared/bench/*.json          # nexus owner of shared bench SSOT (anima/n6 follower)
  self-modify-deny shared/bench/*.jsonl

  # SSOTs META MAY directly observe (read + propose-via-state-flip):
  self-modify-allow design/kick/*.json          # per-cycle witnesses (append-only via witness_emit)
  self-modify-allow state/**/*.jsonl            # raw 77 audit ledgers (append-only)
  self-modify-allow state/proposals/inventory.json  # proposal-locus (apply-gate routed)
  self-modify-allow state/kick/runs/**          # per-kick run artifacts

  # routes for proposals:
  proposal-locus state/proposals/inventory.json
  apply-gate human-approval

  why nexus IS a meta-engine — atlas_meta_dashboard, drill_batch, ω-cycle 자기-발견. 명시적 boundary 없이는 자율적인 .raw/.own/.meta 수정이 failure mode. raw 13 ai-tool-config-ban 과 동일 가족.
  scope tool/meta_*.hexa + atlas_meta_dashboard.md + tool/lockdown/*
  proof state/proposals/inventory.json (forward — schema seed needed)
  proof tool/lockdown/meta_lockdown.hexa
  follow-up tool/meta_lint.hexa — validate self-modify-allow/deny declarations against runtime ω-cycle attempted writes

meta-engine-types 1 new "registered META engines in nexus"
  slug meta-engine-types-canonical
  enforce-layer hive-agent

  engine-type atlas-meta-dashboard
  engine-impl atlas_meta_dashboard.md + state/atlas_health/*.jsonl + tool/atlas_meta_*.hexa
  loop-condition every-kick-completion
  brainstorm-depth shallow

  engine-type ω-cycle (= kick)
  engine-impl tool/kick_dispatch.hexa + design/kick/*.json + state/kick/registry/*
  loop-condition manual-trigger (per .guide workflow 1-10)
  auto-mode-safety FORBIDDEN — autonomous kick fan-out 금지 (오늘 incident: parent-sid 없이 3 parallel 발사 → workflow violation)
  brainstorm-depth deep

  engine-type drill-batch
  engine-impl tool/drill_batch.hexa + tool/drill_breakthrough_runner.hexa
  loop-condition manual-trigger or cron-cadence (daily)
  brainstorm-depth deep
  ttl-per-run 7200

  engine-type roadmap-engine
  engine-impl tool/roadmap_engine.hexa (TOC+A*+Bellman+Brent+Wright+Shannon-Fano)
  loop-condition on-demand or cron-cadence (daily reconcile)
  brainstorm-depth medium
  why production scheduler (32K LOC ecosystem). hive 의 .roadmap + .convergence ↔ nexus 의 math owner.

  engine-type lockdown-meta-lockdown
  engine-impl tool/lockdown/meta_lockdown.hexa
  loop-condition triggered on policy-violation detection
  why hard-stop gate — META 가 자기 boundary 위반하려 할 때 lock kick.

  why nexus 의 primary 작업 IS meta-discovery; 명시적 catalog 가 future ω-cycle 의 새 META engine 등록 강제 (without registration → failure).
  scope tool/meta_*.hexa + tool/lockdown/* + cli/run.hexa kick/drill/omega/roadmap subcommands
  proof tool/kick_dispatch.hexa
  proof tool/drill_batch.hexa
  proof tool/roadmap_engine.hexa --selftest
  proof atlas_meta_dashboard.md

